Jessie-Ann Friend https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Jessie-Ann_Friend 0 Jessie-Ann Friend was born on October 17, 1981 in Escondido, California, USA as Jessie-Ann Jo Friend. She is an actress, known for General Hospital (1963), Magic Island (1995) and Frankie Starlight (1995).
